  <official_title>Phase IIA Trial to Investigate the Optimal Way of Administration (Based on the Immunological, Clinical and Neuroradiological Effects) of Autologous Mesenchymal Bone Marrow Stem Cells (MSC) in Active and Progressive Multiple Sclerosis (MS)</official_title>
