  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to to evaluate the optimal dosage and the way of administration
      of autologous mesenchymal bone marrow stem cells (MSC) either in maximal proximity of the
      lesions in the CNS or by intrathecal injection to the CSF.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
